      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@waldyrious The &quot;goal&quot; of a &quot;plugin&quot; is a concept. It is implemented using a &quot;mojo&quot;.  The &quot;mojo&quot;, in its compiled form, resides in the jar corresponding of the plugin. Same thing, different levels of abstraction."
