  "title" : "What is MOJO in Maven?",
  "body" : "<p>I'm reading about Maven right now and everywhere in a text I see this word (mojo). I approximately understand what it means, but I would not refuse from a good explanation. I tried to google, but found only non-maven explanations.</p>\n\n<p>POJO - ok, but MOJO? Maven Old Java Object?</p>\n"
